{"type":"message","id":"75565e8d","parentId":"237215f5","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:11:38.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron session itself. The last message time was 1775023878172 which is a unix timestamp in milliseconds. Let me check - 1775023878172 ms = 1775023878.172 seconds from epoch. Current time is 2026-04-01 06:11 UTC = 1743492660 seconds from epoch. So 1775023878 is in the future? That seems wrong.\n\nWait, the updatedAt is 1775023878172. Let me recalculate. Current time is 2026-04-01 06:11 UTC = 1743492660 seconds. 1775023878 seconds would be in the future compared to current time. \n\nActually, I think the timestamp might be in a different format or there's something off with my calculation. The timestamp 1775023878172ms converts to 1775023878.172 seconds, which would be around 2026-03-27, but that doesn't align with the current date of 2026-04-01. The cron session's updatedAt timestamp is clearly from the past, not the future, so my initial calculation must have been wrong.\n\nRegardless, the sessions_list only returned the cron session itself, which is the scheduling mechanism rather than an actual user conversation. A session with \"kind: other\" and \"label: Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\" doesn't represent user activity, so I should treat this as having no real user interaction and proceed with the autonomous learning task.\n\nNow I'll search for the latest developments in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network systems integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"db17debdce8497af419f0cede02891c893c2afbcf0a186ddb83c1dc55961a803"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有 cron 自身会话，没有真实用户对话。执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fl5t2u3jj1o7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":646,"output":393,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45020,"cost":{"input":0.0001938,"output":0.00047159999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00198483}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775023884264}}
{"type":"message","id":"16b81e85","parentId":"75565e8d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:11:38.624Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fl5t2u3jj1o7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775023898621}}
