{"type":"message","id":"3aed6aa2","parentId":"ac2fa695","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:13:17.643Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The learning notes have been updated successfully. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"fc49e55491c448f1f76fcfac1c8b762749e1912642903a92e9802dab105c44b5"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n✅ 自主学习任务完成\n\n**执行情况**：\n- 当前无活跃用户对话（仅cron自身会话），触发自主学习\n- 完成3个方向搜索：企业数字化转型、智能安防、IT运维服务\n- 整理5条关键新洞察并追加到 `memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**本次新增核心内容**：\n1. **数据局补贴**：5000万以上项目最高补贴15%（5000万封顶）\n2. **AI规模化**：千个工业智能体+500个典型场景，AI从高端走向中小企业标配\n3. **安防技术突破**：多模态大模型+边缘智能，误报率0.8%，准确率97%+\n4. **运维市场爆发**：2026-2030年CAGR 11.2%，2030年突破5400亿元\n5. **运维新范式**：Agentic AIOps/AgentOps，工程师向\"场景处置专家\"转型\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6955,"output":222,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51158,"cost":{"input":0.0020865,"output":0.00026639999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036723299999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775023989572}}
